      "writtenOn": "2016-08-04T16:20:52Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see the potential leakage. Thanks for catching this. But, I think just making this static is the appropriate thing (Done). Global LazyInstance variables (some without static in front of them either) have been the convention all over, and I\u0027d like to maintain consistency. Plus, I like to avoid class C { \u003cC member or something defined with C\u003e }; when possible.",
